quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  2,106,hum jis aayat ko mansookh kar dete ya usay faramosh kara dete hain to is se behtar ya waisi hi aur aayat bhaij dete hain.kiya tum nahi jantay ke khuda har baat par Qadir hai
  2,107,"tumhe maloom nahi ke asmano aur zameen ki badshahat khuda hi ki hai, aur khuda ke siwa tumhara koi dost aur madad gaar nahi"
  2,108,"kiya tum yeh chahtay ho ke apne paighambar se isi terhan ke sawal karo, jis terhan ke sawal pehlay moose se kiye gay they. aur jis shakhs ne imaan ( chore kar is ) ke badlay kufar liya, woh seedhay raste se bhatak gaya"
  2,109,bohat se ahal kitaab apne dil ki jalan se yeh chahtay hain ke imaan laa chikane ke baad tum ko phir kafir bana den. halaank un par haq zahir ho chuka hai. to tum maaf kardo aur dar guzar karo. yahan taq ke khuda apna ( dosra ) hukum beje. be shak khuda har baat par Qadir hai
  2,110,"aur namaz ada karte raho aur zakaat dete raho. aur jo bhalai apne liye agay bhaij rakho ge, is ko khuda ke haan pa lau ge. kuch shak nahi ke khuda tumahray sab kamon ko dekh raha hai"
  2,111,aur ( yahodi aur isaai ) kehte hain ke yahudion aur esaion ke siwa koi bahisht mein nahi jaane ka. yeh un logon ke khayalat baatil hain. ( ae paighambar un se ) keh do ke agar sachey ho to Daleel paish karo
  2,112,"haan jo shakhs khuda ke agay gardan jhuka day, ( yani imaan le aeye ) aur woh naiko car bhi ho to is ka sila is ke perwar-digaar ke paas hai aur aisay logon ko ( qayamat ke din ) nah kisi terhan ka khauf hoga aur nah woh ghumnaak hon ge"
